</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>None</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Generates pixel data according to DMA pixel data format spec <verbatim>      V1 buffer (Stream1): SMPTE vertical bars (left-to-right)
